&lt;li&gt;Ability to execute on individual projects but still contribute to the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to complete tasks on time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organization, influencing, and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
